{"title":"OYSY问题","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-6122","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\">21世纪出现了一个不世出的大学霸OYSY，她在数学界的权威期刊《OYSY教你学数学》上提出了一个问题，OYSY声称自己是高斯再世，其他人绝对无法解出。当代杰出的数学家肖某和物理学家欢某为这道题苦思冥想了十天十夜，仍然没有头绪。于是他们想到借助计算机来完成这道题，于是请你来帮他们编程解决。问题的内容是这样的：</span></p><p style=\"\"><span style=\"\">已知</span>m<span style=\"\">、</span>n<span style=\"\">为整数，且满足下列两个条件：</span></p><p style=\"\">     ① m<span style=\"\">、</span>n<span style=\"\">∈</span>{<span style=\"\">１，２，</span>…<span style=\"\">，</span>k}<span style=\"\">，即</span>1≤m<span style=\"\">，</span>n≤k</p><p style=\"\">     ②<span style=\"\">（</span>n^2<span style=\"\">－</span>m*n<span style=\"\">－</span>m^2)<span style=\"\">^</span>2<span style=\"\">＝</span>1</p><p>你的任务是：编程输入正整数k（1≤k≤10^9），求一组满足上述两个条件的m、n，并且使m^2＋n^2的值最大。</p><p>例如，从键盘输入k=1995，则输出：m=987   n=1597。</p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>一个正整数k<br></p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>m,n的值<br/></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1995</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p style=\"\">m=987</p><p style=\"\">n=1597</p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Calibri','sans-serif';\">1≤k≤10^9</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}